<p>Billie is in fine spirets lately, He goes down visiting George &amp; Ruth Sippi.</p>
<p>I am continuing this scribble tomorrow because there has been nothing doing for a couple of days.</p>
<p><u>Friday March 24th</u><br/>Billie is plagueing me to take him to a Bazaar to morrow, I suppose I will have to, it is Budden's up at Killara It is for some funds.</p>
